title: Flock Pre-alpha is Open!
message:
Welcome to Flock!

Come and explore, create your own projects, and start getting involved chatting with others about their projects!

title: v1.0.1 Launch Notes
message:
This is the first version of Flock.

Following are the initial pre-alpha features and features coming soon.

features
- discover projects
- create a user
- like and follow projects
- create projects
- add and edit project details
- make projects public
- create channel posts
- comment on channel posts

coming soon
- editing posts
- liking posts
- editing profile
- adding project team members
- adding and editing channels
- extended image library
- uploading project images
- adding profile image
- posting images
- setting username and password
- reseting password
- messaging
- nofications
- and much more!

title: Welcome to Flock!
message:
Welcome to the first version of Flock.

Please explore, create some projects start chatting and sharing ideas!


Post any issues and bugs you find in the #Issues channel and share your ideas and feature suggestions for the platform in the #Ideas channel.
